profile:
Established in 2016, Lincoln Property Maintenance is a small business based in Pickering Village (Ajax), Ontario that thrives on customer satisfaction and professionalism. We understand that owning a property comes with many responsibilities and jobs that can be overwhelming. Our main goal is to help make some of those jobs easier and stress-free. We offer a wide-range of services. 



Owner Ian De Clute has over 15 years of experience in general contracting in the Greater Toronto Area. He works extensively with property owners and managers on residential, condominium, and commercial properties. Ian works together with his clients to understand their needs and develop customized solutions that best achieve clients' goals and satisfaction. Ian prides himself on professionalism and attention to detail to achieve high-quality results.



Please contact us for more information - we'd love to hear from you!


Experienced property maintenance service and general contractor serving homeowners and property management companies in Durham Region, Ontario.

Visit us at www.lincolnpropertymaintenance.ca
